# DEPLOYMENT_CHECKLIST.mdc
## Pre-Deployment Verification Checklist

THIS CHECKLIST MUST BE COMPLETED BEFORE ANY PRODUCTION DEPLOYMENT.
Do not deploy until all items are verified.

---

## 1. Environment Variables

### Verify All Required Env Vars Are Set

Check deployment platform (Vercel, etc.) → Project → Settings → Environment Variables

| Variable | Set? | Correct Value? |
|----------|------|----------------|
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL` | [ ] | [ ] |
| [Add project-specific vars] | [ ] | [ ] |

### Environment-Specific Values

| Environment | URL Format |
|-------------|------------|
| Production | `https://domain.com` |
| Preview | Platform preview URLs |
| Development | `http://localhost:3000` |

### Common Mistakes
- [ ] No trailing slashes on URLs
- [ ] No `http://` when should be `https://`
- [ ] No localhost URLs in production

---

## 2. Link Verification

### Internal Links
- [ ] All navigation links work
- [ ] All footer links work
- [ ] All breadcrumb links work
- [ ] All CTA buttons link to correct pages
- [ ] All "Learn more" links work
- [ ] No 404 errors on any page

### Cross-Site Links (If Monorepo)
- [ ] All cross-site links work
- [ ] Links use config, not hardcoded URLs

### External Links
- [ ] All external links open in new tab
- [ ] All external links have `rel="noopener"`
- [ ] External links go to correct destinations
- [ ] No broken external links

### Contact Links
- [ ] Phone links work (`tel:+1XXXXXXXXXX`)
- [ ] Email links work (`mailto:...`)
- [ ] Map/directions links work

---

## 3. SEO Verification

### Meta Tags (Check Every Page)
- [ ] Every page has unique title (50-60 chars)
- [ ] Every page has unique description (150-160 chars)
- [ ] Canonical URLs are correct (production domain)
- [ ] Open Graph tags present and correct
- [ ] Twitter Card tags present

### Structured Data
- [ ] JSON-LD schema on all pages
- [ ] Schema validates in Rich Results Test
- [ ] No schema errors or warnings
- [ ] BreadcrumbList on all non-homepage pages
- [ ] FAQPage schema where FAQ exists

### Technical SEO
- [ ] `sitemap.xml` generates correctly
- [ ] `robots.txt` is correct
- [ ] No `noindex` on pages that should be indexed
- [ ] Canonical URLs point to production domain

---

## 4. Assets & Media

### Images
- [ ] All images load correctly
- [ ] No broken image links
- [ ] All images have alt text
- [ ] OG images exist (1200x630px)
- [ ] Images are optimized (WebP/AVIF)

### Fonts
- [ ] Custom fonts load correctly
